data.title: List of Imperial Japanese Navy admirals
data.text:
This is a dynamic list and may never be able to satisfy particular standards for completeness. You can help by adding missing items with reliable sources.

The following is a list of the Admirals of the Imperial Japanese Navy during its existence from 1868 until 1945.[1][2][3]

This colour along with the * (asterisk) indicates that the promotion was posthumous.
